title: Ultimate Fantastic Four Vol. 6 (Hardcover)
description:
Stories packed with supernatural surprises and all-out action! When the FF help out with the excavation of the Mole Man’s underground city, they awaken something that should have been left sleeping! Just who is Agatha Harkness, and what are Salem’s Seven? New Ultimate characters! Plus: Someone has the hots for the Human Torch! Also, who are the newest Ultimate X-Men? Does Ultimate Spider-Man have more clones than the regular Spidey? Was Ultimate Thor delusional, or was he really a god? All these questions and more will be answered in the new Ultimate Universe Handbook. And remember - this is the only book guaranteed to give you the Ultimate Six Pack! Collecting ULTIMATE FANTASTIC FOUR #54-57, OFFICIAL HANDBOOK OF THE ULTIMATE MARVEL UNIVERSE #1-2 and ULTIMATE SECRETS.
Rated A …$34.99
ISBN: 978-0-7851-3781-8
